The community of Dobsonville, Soweto, is outraged after another body was discovered along an open veld in the area. #Dstv403 JOHANNESBURG - The community of Dobsonville, Soweto, is outraged after another body was discovered along an open veld in the area. Residents say it's not the first time a murder has occurred in the area in the past few months. READ: Pupil arrested for fatal stabbing The community will be marching to what they've now dubbed 'the crime hotspot'. They plan to hold a short prayer and a wreath-laying ceremony in the area.